name: Chimichanga Peligroso "Orange Blast"
description: Chimichanga Peligroso "Orange Blast" comes fresh out of the oven to celebrate "El dia de los muertos" show at Gigantic Gallery, in Portland. I also kept a few to sell em in order to celebrate the opening of my store!. Chimichanga will keep bad spirits away from your home or office. Is here to protect you and you beloved ones, as the best luchador you could get! This is a limited edition poster (50 copies total) 35 of which are "legal lime" green and only 15 comes in "Orange blast" orange! Screen printed, hand pulled, 275gsm A2 (18x24in) size , ready to frame, ships in tube! stickers and buttons on all orders!
